name: Concentra Alteryx Training
body:
### Welcome to Alteryx Training
This web page serves as the online home for all data and workflows required to complete our Fundamentals and Advanced trainings for Alteryx Designer 10.  

You must download the entire repository of information for the training session as one ZIP file. 

Click the link for the repository.

Click "Download ZIP" from the right-hand side of the screen to download everything you need.

![DownloadZip](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ConcentraUK/ConcentraUK.github.io/master/downloadzip.png)


### Fundamentals
 
Please access the repository [here](https://github.com/ConcentraUK/AlteryxFundamentals).  


### Advanced

Please access the repository [here](https://github.com/ConcentraUK/AlteryxAdvanced).
